basics.name: Cynthia Dwayne
basics.label: Senior Software Developer
basics.summary: Results-driven Senior Software Developer with 12+ years of experience in full-stack development, cloud technologies, and agile methodologies. Proven track record in developing scalable, well-documented code, leading successful migrations, and optimizing system performance. Passionate about creating efficient, user-centric solutions, mentoring junior developers, and driving innovation in high-growth environments.
